{"tid":779338,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貝碧嘉襲港】澳門晚上7時半改掛8號風球","createTime":"2018-08-14T10:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T12:44:09.000Z","uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04638f00df91ac944cb574df178e336f7b96bd01","tid":779338,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:35:52.000Z","msg":"三號強風信號現正生效，香港天文台預計，傍晚6時前改發八號烈風或暴風信號的機會較低，並會視乎風暴的動向及本港風力變化，考慮在今晚是否需要更改信號。不過較為靠近風暴的澳門，其氣象局預計當地將會增強，將於晚上7時30分改掛8號東北風球。<br />\n<br />\n澳門氣象局表示，貝碧嘉下午4時集結在澳門以南約120公里，向偏北方向移動，逐漸迫近澳門。由於橋上風力間中達到強風程度及有陣風，呼籲駕駛人士注意行車安全，電單車駕駛者應使用西灣大橋電單車專道。<br />\n<br />\n此外，藍色風暴潮警告亦仍然生效，由於今日仍然適逢天文大潮，加上風力較大，潮汐水位將高於內港路面。"},{"pid":"2a2ef1496394b8938d82ef43e828b179d8fcf71c","tid":779338,"uid":14719,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/225851_1a8f73627b1f1199325eca06379c652c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F225851_1a8f73627b1f1199325eca06379c652c.jpg&h=7a7d9d11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d6b7c635aea055ed140444f516aee410a8071d4","tid":779338,"uid":180156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"澳門依家跟本有小小風都8號<br />\n廢事比人屌唔掛8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035342b0877e0e61d7c8dbdc45ddb843fac997fa","tid":779338,"uid":113178,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9d6b7c635aea055ed140444f516aee410a8071d4","tid":779338,"uid":180156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"澳門依家跟本有小小風都8號<br />\n廢事比人屌唔掛8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:39:38.000Z","msg":"變咗驚弓之鳥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgm